# Financial Modeling Prep (FMP) API key — used by the Portfolio page for live
# quotes (15-min delayed) and 1-year EOD history.
#
# Sign up for a free key at:
#   https://site.financialmodelingprep.com/developer/docs
#
# Free tier limits: ~250 calls/day, batch endpoints capped at 5 symbols/request,
# US equities only (a small symbol-override map handles non-US holdings — see
# src/app/data/portfolioHoldings.ts).
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the value below.
VITE_FMP_API_KEY=your_fmp_api_key_here

# Dropbox app key — used by the Resources page "Dropbox" tab to embed a shared
# folder via the official Dropbox Embedder SDK.
#
# Setup:
#   1. Create an app at https://www.dropbox.com/developers/apps
#      - API: Scoped access
#      - Type: App folder OR Full Dropbox
#   2. On the app's settings page, under "Chooser/Saver/Embedder domains",
#      add every origin that will load the embed (e.g. `localhost`,
#      `cams.example.com`).
#   3. Copy the "App key" into VITE_DROPBOX_APP_KEY below.
VITE_DROPBOX_APP_KEY=your_dropbox_app_key_here
